# cellState()

**Instance Method**

Returns the current cell state of the receiver.

## Declaration

```swift
func cellState() -> IKImageBrowserCellState
```

## Return Value

The current state of the cell. See [doc://com.apple.quartz/documentation/Quartz/IKImageBrowserCellState] for possible values.

## Discussion

The [doc://com.apple.quartz/documentation/Quartz/IKImageBrowserView] creates thumbnails asynchronously. This method returns the current state.
